{"tid":1247072,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［勇武可智取］金鐘國情義結 唔好請君入甕","createTime":"2019-06-21T03:44:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T07:19:45.000Z","uid":186,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ae3efbaa201de22cb4899221b6c6978a7ad53215","tid":1247072,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T03:44:05.000Z","msg":"雨傘一代 對金鐘國都有情義結<br />\n佔有金鐘國就得天下 但其實成敗金鐘國 <br />\n班狗就請君入甕 引你佔<br />\n一 佔就無得be water 數字兵力一眼睇哂<br />\n二 目標為咩 佔有金鐘國 影響市民<br />\n政府有應急機制 去第二到開工<br />\n損己利人<br />\n三 五大訴求 關金鐘國咩事<br />\n     有狗竇 有禮拜虎 <br />\n<br />\n請大家勇武 和理非時都要智取<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n畀人有勇無謀嘅感覺就唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XrVERvB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXrVERvB.png&h=c760c359&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kNcDnCh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkNcDnCh.png&h=becff183&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CH1HPhj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCH1HPhj.png&h=0ef6b76c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f28dd7ae328d88abdcf6e171e52749f303b7c102","tid":1247072,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T03:44:16.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"4b897a6b7734b3bb730c3211a2e06b436ca1d20a","tid":1247072,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T03:44:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cccaa5e25ef691ce33be6168e222b4ad6af2bcd3","tid":1247072,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T03:44:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"363f86c189c3d5b38e8aa622b2ea02e7a4baa8c1","tid":1247072,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21